ActCourts Administration Service Act
PrecisConfirm that RAYMOND P. GUENETTE of Ottawa, Ontario, a Deputy Chief Administrator, may continue to act as Chief Administrator of the Courts Administration Service, for the period commencing on December 3, 2004 and terminating on June 3, 2005.
